{"tid":1604901,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"南華早報消息稱，習近平批准林鄭月娥撤回修訂逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:28:15.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"270766244ebcf6c0d3530bf9dd2e1261569160bd","tid":1604901,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"《南華早報》引述接近特區政府的消息人士報道，<strong>行政長官林鄭月娥宣布正式撤回修訂逃犯條例草案前，獲國家主席習近平批准。</strong><br />\n<br />\n報道說，林鄭月娥今個月4日正式宣布撤回修例前不久，上報習近平的辦公室審議，並獲得批准，<strong>又說由於撤回修例是至關重要的決定，與任命特區政府主要官員一樣，因此需要習近平的批准。</strong><br />\n<br />\n消息人士又說，北京考慮到中美關係的背景下，今次事件不再單純是特區政府與北京之間的問題，特區政府在如何處理修例引發的政治危機方面，並無太多迴旋餘地。<br />\n<br />\n另一名消息人士就說，<strong>從國家安全的角度去看，事件不是特區政府範圍內處理的問題，由習近平批准如此重要的決定，是自然及符合邏輯的做法。</strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥是在今個月4日發表電視講話，宣布正式撤回條例，北京表示理解，並尊重特區政府的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483018-20190928.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483018-20190928.htm&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1ZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=738c9ae9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483018-20190928.htm&h=a9993114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483018-20190928.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b5b3eb47edc50f8e9fdd43b405a56e1fb5c44910","tid":1604901,"uid":140452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"撤?<br />\n五大訴求呀撤"},{"pid":"c3f9a3772c85deab778e8c1014258a87d65c0aef","tid":1604901,"uid":69741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"成個月啦喎，仲講d咁舊既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a2ac254a16828cebafc7f18c110b204b5806c5","tid":1604901,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5b3eb47edc50f8e9fdd43b405a56e1fb5c44910","tid":1604901,"uid":140452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"撤?<br />\n五大訴求呀撤"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"重點係今次認左，逃犯修訂條例，係中央政府干預香港。"},{"pid":"e34f9e35313cabfdfa76e218472ab7d881a2fa20","tid":1604901,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3f9a3772c85deab778e8c1014258a87d65c0aef","tid":1604901,"uid":69741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"成個月啦喎，仲講d咁舊既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"之前係林鄭話要撤<br />\n今次中央approve左"},{"pid":"b801a7f396ce9b2913487cb1b76fae9e06a98935","tid":1604901,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"香港已完全失去港人治港 高度自治<br />\n一國兩制如同虛設 行政已主導立法同司法"},{"pid":"bfe57d284cf48a405c9d691e64295c67f426c979","tid":1604901,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"又係南早. 咩料都係南早先放. 究竟南早係咩background?"},{"pid":"01f064b4b48b65f8c733aae04558d23a129c6032","tid":1604901,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"理閪佢"},{"pid":"dc4148a7e091b1a732f88e5dbd7914e72a21f56b","tid":1604901,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a2ac254a16828cebafc7f18c110b204b5806c5","tid":1604901,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5b3eb47edc50f8e9fdd43b405a56e1fb5c44910","tid":1604901,"uid":140452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"撤?<br />\n五大訴求呀撤"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"重點係今次認左，逃犯修訂條例，係中央政府干預香港。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:15:02.000Z","msg":"文宣重點應該立即轉去北京破壞一國兩制，港人自決2047前途問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e48a758f3b00cad38376b08800735273561d60","tid":1604901,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a2ac254a16828cebafc7f18c110b204b580